<plot>Charlie believes in love at first sight and from the moment his eyes fixed on Brenda, he knew she had to be his girl. Now, Charlie must find a way to express his true feelings and overcome all obstacles on his way to winning Brenda's heart. Charlie's past relationships have never gone his way, but he is bound and determined to make this one work. Will Charlie be able to move on from his failed and buried relationships? And, will Brenda be his happily ever after or will she just be another victim of love? Crazy Love is a disturbingly wicked spin on the traditional thriller meets screwball romantic comedy.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?118028</url></doc>
